The SSG08 bolt-action is a low-damage but very cost-effective sniper rifle, making it a smart choice for early-round long-range marksmanship. It has been custom painted with a monstrosity comprised of green tentacles, teeth, and one eyeball. All the better to see you with
Sticker: Renegades (Holo) | 2020 RMR
More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. A custom painted M4 showing its internals with an X-Ray
Sticker: Fnatic | Katowice 2014, Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2015, Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2014, Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2015

With a smaller magazine than its unmuffled counterpart, the silenced M4A1 provides quieter shots with less recoil and better accuracy. It has been custom painted with a beastly creature in psychedelic colors. You really want to impress me Booth? Make this black light sensitive - Rona Sabri, Rising Star
Sticker: Ninjas in Pyjamas (Holo) | Paris 2023, Ninjas in Pyjamas (Holo) | Paris 2023, Ninjas in Pyjamas (Holo) | Paris 2023, Ninjas in Pyjamas (Holo) | Paris 2023

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. It has been custom painted with the image of a creature made of water in a graphic style.
This is a collectible pin commemorating Half-Life: Alyx, Valve's VR return to the Half-Life series. It can be displayed on your CS:GO profile.
This is a Series 3 collectible pin. It can be displayed on your CS:GO profile.

Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. A brightly colored paint job inspired by street art has been applied. "Inside voices, please"

A cheap option for cash-strapped players, the FAMAS effectively fills the niche between more expensive rifles and the less-effective SMGs. It has been custom painted gold and features various details celebrating 20 years of Counter-Strike. Here's to 20 more

An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been custom painted with totally radical blue and pink highlights. Available for 4 easy payments of $124.95!
As expensive as it is powerful, the Desert Eagle is an iconic pistol that is difficult to master but surprisingly accurate at long range. It has been hand engraved and inlaid with a scroll pattern.
Sticker: Fearsome (Holo), Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2014, Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2015, Ninjas in Pyjamas | Katowice 2015

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. An acrylic painting of Mount Fuji at dawn has been applied. The painting is used as a pattern, so each weapon may appear different. The red sun rises
Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has been painted with a hydrographic pattern of nuclear hazards symbols.

A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. It has been custom painted with circular motifs. This one is steeped in tradition and blood

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been painted using metallic effect paints and given a wavy pattern using a rubber comb tool. Bright colors hide a gun with a dark purpose
This item commemorates the 2022 PGL Antwerp CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Quarterfinal match between Ninjas in Pyjamas and FaZe Clan.

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. A blue spiral pattern has been applied to the slide. Hard to miss
Sticker: PGL (Gold) | Antwerp 2022, Inferno (Gold), Ninjas in Pyjamas (Gold) | Antwerp 2022, FaZe Clan (Gold) | Antwerp 2022
This item commemorates the 2021 PGL Stockholm CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Semifinal match between Natus Vincere and Gambit Esports.

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has been painted using a purple Digital Disruptive Pattern (DDPAT) hydrographic. By the time you're close enough to notice the pixels it's already too late
Sticker: FaZe Clan | Antwerp 2022, ropz | Antwerp 2022, ropz | Antwerp 2022, ropz | Antwerp 2022
This item commemorates the BLAST.tv Paris 2023 CS:GO Championship.

High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. A striking green and blue bush viper has been hand painted over a black base. As deadly as it is beautiful
An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design.

The Negev is a beast that can keep the enemy at bay with its pin-point supressive fire, provided you have the luxury of time to gain control over it. It has been custom painted with a hydrographic reminiscent of heavy machinery. Feared by Queens. Beloved by Bishops.

This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
Composer Matt Levine delivers raw swagger in this gritty homage to the Spaghetti Western. It has never felt better to say, "go ahead, make my day..."
This is a Series 3 collectible pin. It can be displayed on your CS:GO profile.

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has been painted white and given a stark red magazine. Perfect for shooting toasters
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

The SCAR-20 is a semi-automatic sniper rifle that trades a high rate of fire and powerful long-distance damage for sluggish movement speed and big price tag. It has been hand painted using a blue theme to resemble an architect's blueprint. The best-laid plans are drawn to scale
This item commemorates the BLAST.tv Paris 2023 CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.
The Bizon SMG is low-damage, but offers a uniquely designed high-capacity drum magazine that reloads quickly. Parts of the weapon have been replaced with brass. Fool's gold

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a red and black color scheme. Great on cars, better on weapons

A cheap option for cash-strapped players, the FAMAS effectively fills the niche between more expensive rifles and the less-effective SMGs. It has been spray-painted freehand using mesh fabric as a stencil.

The pricy G3SG1 lowers movement speed considerably but compensates with a higher rate of fire than other sniper rifles. A green forest gives way to a blue sky at the center of this custom paint job. "There, a clearing in the forest!"

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. Phoenix faction logos have been spray painted over its white and red base. They're bringing in the big guns

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat. Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread
This item commemorates the 2022 PGL Antwerp CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Grand Final match between Natus Vincere and FaZe Clan.

Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. The slide features a teal hydrographic pattern of interweaving pipes. A handheld heat rejection device
Sticker: Natus Vincere (Gold) | Antwerp 2022, FaZe Clan (Gold) | Antwerp 2022, PGL (Gold) | Antwerp 2022, Nuke (Gold)

The SSG08 bolt-action is a low-damage but very cost-effective sniper rifle, making it a smart choice for early-round long-range marksmanship. A high tech custom paint job of blues and purples has been applied. What secrets does _001 hold?

The Nova's rock-bottom price tag makes it a great ambush weapon for a cash-strapped team. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a red and black color scheme. Great on cars, better on weapons

Powerful and accurate, the AUG scoped assault rifle compensates for its long reload times with low spread and a high rate of fire. A custom paint job with gunmetal triangles and carbon fiber over a burnt orange base. All things being equal

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. A toxic, pale blue hydrographic pattern has been applied. Hypotheses are never proven
This item commemorates the 2021 PGL Stockholm CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Semifinal match between Natus Vincere and Gambit Esports.

The SSG08 bolt-action is a low-damage but very cost-effective sniper rifle, making it a smart choice for early-round long-range marksmanship. It has been spray-painted with a rust colored zebra stripe pattern. Eat, sleep, hunt, repeat
Sticker: Gambit Gaming (Gold) | Stockholm 2021, Mirage (Gold), Natus Vincere (Gold) | Stockholm 2021, PGL (Gold) | Stockholm 2021

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil. True power is demonstrated with subtle application

Firing two large-mag Berettas at once will lower accuracy and increase load times. On the bright side, you'll get to fire two large-mag Berettas at once. It has individual parts spray-painted tan, navy and dark green. Rona Sabri still hasn't forgiven Sebastien for not selecting her to go after Turner
